blogPost.excerpt:
Battlefield™ 2042 is available on November 19, 2021

Be among the first to experience the next generation of all-out warfare in the Battlefield 2042 Open Beta. Join the fight on Orbital with a diverse selection of Specialists, cutting-edge weaponry, and vehicles to choose from. Open Beta between October 6-9, 2021. Early access is available on October 6-7, 2021 for all players who pre-order the game or are current EA Play members. 

Preload starts Oct 5th, 2021 at 06:00 UTC on PC and 07:00 UTC on consoles.

Find out more about the Open Beta including PC requirements, controls, and more here: http://x.ea.com/69873

Battlefield 2042 is a first-person shooter that marks the return to the iconic all-out warfare of the franchise. Adapt and overcome in a near-future world transformed by disorder. Squad up and bring a cutting-edge arsenal into dynamically-changing battlegrounds supporting 128 players*, unprecedented scale, and epic destruction.

Pre-order now for early access to the Open Beta and more: http://x.ea.com/68944 

Find out more about Battlefield: http://x.ea.com/68900

See the Battlefield 2042 Official Reveal Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ASzOzrB-a9E

See the Battlefield 2042 Official Gameplay Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WomAGoEh-Ss 

See the Battlefield Portal Official Trailer
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q4qWMcQfOCc

See the Battlefield 2042 Exodus Short Film
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FJVCfhLEYdo

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/battlefield
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/battlefield
Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/battlefield

#Battlefield #Battlefield2042 #WeAreNoPats
*Supported on Xbox Series X|S, PC and PlayStation®5. Xbox One and PlayStation®4 will be locked at 64 players

previous.excerpt:
She brings light and life to a realm of darkness and death. 
 
The Hour of the Witch Chapter is coming to Dead by Daylight this October. It includes a new original Survivor, Mikaela Reid. Writing horror stories is her favorite pastime, and Halloween her favorite holiday. Did we mention she also has a keen interest in witchcraft?  

Prepare for the Hour of the Witch by sharpening your skills in Dead by Daylight today.  


PLAY DEAD BY DAYLIGHT: https://buythegame.deadbydaylight.com  

Dead by Daylight is a multiplayer action/horror game where one player takes on the role of a brutal Killer and the other four play as Survivors. As a Killer your goal is to sacrifice as many Survivors as possible. As Survivors your goal is to work together to evade, escape, and most importantly – stay alive.   

Join the official forum: https://forum.deadbydaylight.com/en   


Like and follow us on our official Social Media Channels:        

- Facebook: https://facebook.com/DeadByDaylight    
- Twitter:  https://twitter.com/deadbybhvr     
- Instagram:  https://instagram.com/deadbydaylight      

#DbD #HourOfTheWitch
